text: Jorge Fernando Pinheiro de Jesus (; born 24 July 1954) is a Portuguese professional football manager and former player. He is the current manager of Al Hilal in the Saudi Pro League. In March 2020, Jesus tested positive for COVID-19. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese footballers Category:Portuguese football managers Category:Al Hilal SFC managers
